- But today is a kind of
second introductory lecture

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:16.530
where we're gonna be thinking about

00:00:16.530 --> 00:00:20.940
the origins of the nation in
particular, as with last time,

00:00:20.940 --> 00:00:23.160
I'm gonna toss you some
what I think are softballs,

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:26.640
but also feel free to raise
